title: Nicole Remund
text: Nicole Corinne Remund (born 31 December 1989) is a Swiss <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="defender%20%28soccer%29">defender</a>, currently playing for <a href="FC%20Z%C3%BCrich%20Frauen">FC Zürich Frauen</a>. She is a member of the <a href="Switzerland%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Swiss national team</a> since 2008.
